{"tid":1392474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國議息】聯儲局減息四分一厘","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T01:47:12.000Z","uid":26418,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d57d51b67909c1d5a0df4fc8d8bfed448b1b3663","tid":1392474,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190801/59883279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59883279&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=5fdeb439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59883279&h=b9f69456\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190801/59883279</a><br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局結束一連兩日議息會議，一如市場預期減四分一厘，聯邦基金利率由2.25厘至2.5厘，減至2厘至2.25厘。<br />\n<br />\n儲局自2015年12月展開加息周期後，採取循序漸進加息步伐，連同去年底加息，三年間合共加息9次，累計加幅2.25厘。今次減息，亦是繼2008年12月後，逾十年後再度減息。利率期貨顯示，下次9月18日議息會議，減息機會約60%。"},{"pid":"8a9847eeaedd9fad107eb06e90b60b9e66942a49","tid":1392474,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:08:58.000Z","msg":"牛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efd1c6493fbb6162360b1f65f40a50f680be478","tid":1392474,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"預期內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 消化哂啦"},{"pid":"188429b5d3454566c7a5efd74b80c3b51d2829c0","tid":1392474,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:04:12.000Z","msg":"道指跌三百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a547059b6a871a131e1b10c96914cc4f88c58cd","tid":1392474,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4